ie）“准备好！”专辑漆。信用：出版" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/David-Bowie">大卫·鲍伊（David Bowie</a> ）的“准备，套装，去！”的特别版现场专辑将在今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/record-store-day">唱片故事日</a>发行。</p><p> &#39;准备好了，设定，去！ （LIVE，Riverside Studios &#39;03）&#39;将于4月12日通过Parlophone Records发布。限量版Double Vinyl LP和CD将与2025年唱片商店Day合作。这张专辑是Bowie的2003年9月8日的现场录音互动卫星活动在伦敦Hammersmith的Riverside Studios举行。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="大卫·鲍伊（David Bowie） - 新杀手明星（Live，Riverside Studios &#39;03）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sm337XcdmY4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该活动在26个国家 /地区的86家剧院播出，并与鲍伊本人进行了问答环节。这场一次性的音乐会使摇滚偶像表演了他的专辑“真人秀”，这是有史以来第一次。</p><p> “准备好了，固定，走了！”将以鲍伊（Bowie）首次在特别演出中表演的完整的11首歌声以及三首以前未发行的曲目。为了庆祝这一宣布，“新杀手明星”的现场表演已发布。在上面查看。 </p><figure id="attachment_3833731" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833731" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833731" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1.jpg" alt="大卫·鲍伊（David Bowie）“准备好！”专辑漆。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/David-Bowie-Ready-Set-Go-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833731" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·鲍伊（David Bowie）“准备好！”专辑漆。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>大卫·鲍伊（David Bowie）的“准备好，固定，去！ （Live，Riverside Studios &#39;03）轨道列表是：</strong></h3><p><strong>侧1</strong><br /> <strong>“新杀手之星”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Pablo Picasso&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“永远不会老”</strong></p><p><strong>侧2</strong><br /> <strong>“最孤独的家伙”</strong><br /> <strong>“寻找水”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;她会驾驶大型汽车&#39;</strong></p><p><strong>侧3</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;天&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“秋天的狗炸弹”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;尝试一些，买一些&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;现实&#39;</strong></p><p><strong>侧4</strong><br /> <strong>“带我迪斯科王”</strong><br /> <strong>“哈罗太空犬”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;仙人掌&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;害怕的&#39;</strong></p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2025-post-malone-announced-as-ambassador-3831086">马龙最近被宣布为2025年唱片商店日的大使</a>。</p><p>该活动将在整个英国看到超过270家独立的唱片店，以及全球数千个唱片公司，欢迎新的乙烯基发行版，包括一次性LPS和限量版特别版本的过去发行版。与以往一样，还将举办各种各样的店内聚会和庆祝独立唱片商店文化。</p><p>在其他与鲍伊相关的新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/nosferatu-review-faithful-dracula-remake-nicholas-hoult-3819771"><i>诺斯费拉图</i></a>导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/robert-eggers">罗伯特·艾格斯（Robert Eggers）</a>被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/nosferatu-director-robert-eggers-confirmed-to-direct-labyrinth-sequel-3831667">证实要写并导演幻想经典<i>迷宫</i>的续集。</a></p><p>这部原始电影由鲍伊（Bowie）饰演鲍伊（Bowie）饰演哥布林国王（Jareth the Goblin King）和珍妮弗·康纳利（Jennifer Connelly），饰演少年莎拉·威廉姆斯（Sarah Williams），从来没有续集或翻拍，但猜测已经多年了。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-bowie-ready-set-go-live-album-to-be-released-for-record-store-day-2025-3833719">戴维·鲍伊（David Bowie）的职位“准备好了，可以！”现场专辑将在NME上发行，第2025天</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
